comments: Young (ATL) makes marginal contact to Morris Sr.'s (LAC) body after the release of his jump shot attempt.
Leonard (LAC) cleanly blocks Collins' (ATL) jump shot attempt.
Collins (ATL) commits a take foul on Leonard (LAC).
Young (ATL) shuffles his feet upon receiving the throw-in.
Snell (ATL) establishes himself in a screening position in the path of Mann (LAC) and absorbs the contact.
Kennard (LAC) legally contests Young's (ATL) driving shot attempt.
Huerter (ATL) makes marginal contact with Leonard's (LAC) arm and does not affect his ability to gather at the end of his drive.
Hunter (ATL) and George (LAC) make incidental contact with each other during the loose ball.
